System Monitor
This python script monitors overall system health and resources and is easily extendible.
Check the psutil documentation:
	https://psutil.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

Dependencies are some python modules:
    lm-sensors
    python3-rich
    python3-psutil
    python3-readchar

To execute on a Linux system:
    # ./sys_mon.py

    Press 'q' to quit.


